---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.vue';
import Card from '../components/Card.vue';
import Badge from '../components/Badge.vue';
---

<style>
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="Sukun Regenerative Culture - Where Peace Nurtures Life">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden -mt-16 md:-mt-20 pt-16 md:pt-20">
    <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img 
        src="/images/farm.png" 
        alt="Sukun Regenerative Culture - Sylhet Farm" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover brightness-80"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dark-moss/40"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 backdrop-blur-[2px]"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 py-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="hero-title mb-4 animate-fade-in text-white drop-shadow-2xl text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight">
         Sukun Regenerative Culture
        </h1>
        <h2 class="hero-tagline mb-6 animate-fade-in text-white drop-shadow-2xl text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-4xl leading-tight">
          Where Peace Nurtures Life
        </h2>
        
        <p class="hero-description text-base md:text-lg mb-10 text-white/90 drop-shadow-md leading-relaxed tracking-wide  mx-auto">
          A faith-rooted movement for ecological and cultural regeneration in Sylhet. We cultivate inner peace (sukūn) and outward renewal (tajdīd) through education, farming, and stewardship.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <Button href="/projects" client:load>
            Discover More
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ecological + Cultural Themes -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-paper">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-12">Ecological + Cultural Themes</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <Card client:load>
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center text-evergreen"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" class="h-9 w-9" fill="currentColor"><path d="M216-176q-45-45-70.5-104T120-402q0-63 24-124.5T222-642q35-35 86.5-60t122-39.5Q501-756 591.5-759t202.5 7q8 106 5 195t-16.5 160.5q-13.5 71.5-38 125T684-182q-53 53-112.5 77.5T450-80q-65 0-127-25.5T216-176Zm112-16q29 17 59.5 24.5T450-160q46 0 91-18.5t86-59.5q18-18 36.5-50.5t32-85Q709-426 716-500.5t2-177.5q-49-2-110.5-1.5T485-670q-61 9-116 29t-90 55q-45 45-62 89t-17 85q0 59 22.5 103.5T262-246q42-80 111-153.5T534-520q-72 63-125.5 142.5T328-192Zm0 0Zm0 0Z"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Ecological Regeneration</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">
            Through <strong>regenerative farming</strong>, we heal soil, water, and biodiversity
            using permaculture and proper land care.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <Card client:load>
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center text-evergreen"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" class="h-9 w-9" fill="currentColor"><path d="m480-120-58-52q-101-91-167-157T150-447.5Q111-500 95.5-544T80-634q0-94 63-157t157-63q52 0 99 22t81 62q34-40 81-62t99-22q94 0 157 63t63 157q0 46-15.5 90T810-447.5Q771-395 705-329T538-172l-58 52Zm0-108q96-86 158-147.5t98-107q36-45.5 50-81t14-70.5q0-60-40-100t-100-40q-47 0-87 26.5T518-680h-76q-15-41-55-67.5T300-774q-60 0-100 40t-40 100q0 35 14 70.5t50 81q36 45.5 98 107T480-228Zm0-273Z"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Cultural Renewal</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">
            Through <strong>living education</strong>, we renew traditional wisdom and
            faith- and culture-rooted values for resilient, conscious communities.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <Card client:load>
          <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center text-evergreen"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" class="h-9 w-9" fill="currentColor"><path d="M475-160q4 0 8-2t6-4l328-328q12-12 17.5-27t5.5-30q0-16-5.5-30.5T817-607L647-777q-11-12-25.5-17.5T591-800q-15 0-30 5.5T534-777l-11 11 74 75q15 14 22 32t7 38q0 42-28.5 70.5T527-522q-20 0-38.5-7T456-550l-75-74-175 175q-3 3-4.5 6.5T200-435q0 8 6 14.5t14 6.5q4 0 8-2t6-4l136-136 56 56-135 136q-3 3-4.5 6.5T285-350q0 8 6 14t14 6q4 0 8-2t6-4l136-135 56 56-135 136q-3 2-4.5 6t-1.5 8q0 8 6 14t14 6q4 0 7.5-1.5t6.5-4.5l136-135 56 56-136 136q-3 3-4.5 6.5T454-180q0 8 6.5 14t14.5 6Zm-1 80q-37 0-65.5-24.5T375-166q-34-5-57-28t-28-57q-34-5-56.5-28.5T206-336q-38-5-62-33t-24-66q0-20 7.5-38.5T149-506l232-231 131 131q2 3 6 4.5t8 1.5q9 0 15-5.5t6-14.5q0-4-1.5-8t-4.5-6L398-777q-11-12-25.5-17.5T342-800q-15 0-30 5.5T285-777L144-635q-9 9-15 21t-8 24q-2 12 0 24.5t8 23.5l-58 58q-17-23-25-50.5T40-590q2-28 14-54.5T87-692l141-141q24-23 53.5-35t60.5-12q31 0 60.5 12t52.5 35l11 11 11-11q24-23 53.5-35t60.5-12q31 0 60.5 12t52.5 35l169 169q23 23 35 53t12 61q0 31-12 60.5T873-437L545-110q-14 14-32.5 22T474-80Zm-99-560Z"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="mb-3">Community Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">
            Through <strong>community stewardship</strong>, we build ethical livelihoods,
            cooperation, and long-term social–ecological wellbeing.
          </p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Projects -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-mist">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Our Projects — Emerging Initiatives</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal/80 text-lg">
          Three interconnected initiatives are being developed to bring regeneration into daily life.
          Two are in visioning and land-securing phases, and one has just begun implementation.
          Follow our journey as these seeds grow into living realities.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 mb-8">
        <Card client:load>
          <div class="mb-4 -mx-6 -mt-6 overflow-hidden rounded-t-2xl">
            <img 
              src="/images/sukun academy bangladesh.png" 
              alt="Sukun Academy Bangladesh" 
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
          </div>
          <Badge variant="info" client:load>Future Project</Badge>
          <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Sukun Academy — Bangladesh</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-3">
            Status: Concept & land phase
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-4">
            Planned regenerative learning & training centre in Sylhet.
          </p>
          <Button href="/projects/sukun-academy" size="sm" client:load>
            Learn More
          </Button>
        </Card>

        <Card client:load>
          <div class="mb-4 -mx-6 -mt-6 overflow-hidden rounded-t-2xl">
            <img 
              src="/images/al fajr eco village.png" 
              alt="Al Fajr Ecovillage" 
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
          </div>
          <Badge variant="info" client:load>Future Project</Badge>
          <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Al Fajr Ecovillage Jamāʿah</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-3">
            Status: Idea phase
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-4">
            Planned ecovillage demonstrating faith- and culture-rooted regenerative living.
          </p>
          <Button href="/projects/al-fajr-ecovillage" size="sm" client:load>
            Learn More
          </Button>
        </Card>

        <Card client:load>
          <div class="mb-4 -mx-6 -mt-6 overflow-hidden rounded-t-2xl">
            <img 
              src="/images/Darul Hayah Regenerative Farm.png" 
              alt="Darul Hayah Regenerative Farm" 
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300"
            />
          </div>
          <Badge variant="success" client:load>Implementation Started</Badge>
          <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Darul Hayah Regenerative Farm</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 mb-3">
            Status: Early implementation
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-4">
            Early-stage regenerative farm & learning sanctuary.
          </p>
          <Button href="/projects/darul-hayah-farm" size="sm" client:load>
            Learn More
          </Button>
        </Card>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <Button href="/projects" variant="secondary" client:load>
          View All Projects
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Barakah Circular Economy -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-paper">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-card-bg px-8 py-12 shadow-card md:px-12 lg:flex lg:items-start lg:gap-14">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-8 my-auto">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium leading-tight text-charcoal md:text-4xl">
              The Barakah Circular Economy
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
              Sukun and Al Fajr are envisioned to operate under one Community Land Trust (Waqf — sacred commons) and a regenerative livelihood model that keeps resources circulating ethically within the community.
            </p>
          </div>

          <Button href="/get-involved" class="mt-4 mr-4" client:load>
            Support the Waqf
          </Button>

          <Button href="/get-involved" class="mt-4" client:load>
            Become a contributor
          </Button>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 flex-1 space-y-4 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-warm-paper px-6 py-5 shadow-card">
