              <div class="space-y-1">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Waqf</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 !mb-0">Sacred commons stewardship of land and core assets.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-warm-paper px-6 py-5 shadow-card">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-lg text-dark-moss"><svg class="fill-evergreen w-9 h-9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 -960 960 960"  fill="#e8eaed"><path d="M80-120v-80h360v-447q-26-9-45-28t-28-45H240l120 280q0 50-41 85t-99 35q-58 0-99-35t-41-85l120-280h-80v-80h247q12-35 43-57.5t70-22.5q39 0 70 22.5t43 57.5h247v80h-80l120 280q0 50-41 85t-99 35q-58 0-99-35t-41-85l120-280H593q-9 26-28 45t-45 28v447h360v80H80Zm585-320h150l-75-174-75 174Zm-520 0h150l-75-174-75 174Zm335-280q17 0 28.5-11.5T520-760q0-17-11.5-28.5T480-800q-17 0-28.5 11.5T440-760q0 17 11.5 28.5T480-720Z"/></svg></span>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Fairness</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 !mb-0">Fair exchange rooted in contribution.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-warm-paper px-6 py-5 shadow-card">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-lg text-dark-moss"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="fill-evergreen w-9 h-9" viewBox="0 -960 960 960"><path d="m798-322-62-62q44-41 69-97t25-119q0-63-25-118t-69-96l62-64q56 53 89 125t33 153q0 81-33 153t-89 125ZM670-450l-64-64q18-17 29-38.5t11-47.5q0-26-11-47.5T606-686l64-64q32 29 50 67.5t18 82.5q0 44-18 82.5T670-450Zm-310 10q-66 0-113-47t-47-113q0-66 47-113t113-47q66 0 113 47t47 113q0 66-47 113t-113 47ZM40-120v-112q0-33 17-62t47-44q51-26 115-44t141-18q77 0 141 18t115 44q30 15 47 44t17 62v112H40Zm80-80h480v-32q0-11-5.5-20T580-266q-36-18-92.5-36T360-320q-71 0-127.5 18T140-266q-9 5-14.5 14t-5.5 20v32Zm240-320q33 0 56.5-23.5T440-600q0-33-23.5-56.5T360-680q-33 0-56.5 23.5T280-600q0 33 23.5 56.5T360-520Zm0-80Zm0 400Z"/></svg></span>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Participatory Shūrā Governance</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 !mb-0">Consultative ecological leadership.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-warm-paper px-6 py-5 shadow-card">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-lg text-dark-moss"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="fill-evergreen w-9 h-9" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" ><path d="M204-318q-22-38-33-78t-11-82q0-134 93-228t227-94h7l-64-64 56-56 160 160-160 160-56-56 64-64h-7q-100 0-170 70.5T240-478q0 26 6 51t18 49l-60 60ZM481-40 321-200l160-160 56 56-64 64h7q100 0 170-70.5T720-482q0-26-6-51t-18-49l60-60q22 38 33 78t11 82q0 134-93 228t-227 94h-7l64 64-56 56Z"/></svg></span>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Regenerative Reinvestment</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70 !mb-0">Regenerative reinvestment into soil, people, and learning.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

